---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Contact - Atiquzzaman Soikat">
    <!-- Profile Image -->
    <div class="w-full mx-auto md:w-2/5 mb-8">
        <div class="relative">
            <div
                class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-600 rounded-full opacity-10 blur-xl transform scale-110"
            >
            </div>
            <div>
                <img
                    src="https://res.cloudinary.com/theazs/image/upload/w_1000,ar_1:1,c_fill,g_auto,e_art:hokusai/v1745151420/personal-website/E62A0787-01_fwd5qy.jpg"
                    alt="Atiquzzaman Soikat"
                    class="relative w-48 h-48 md:w-64 md:h-64 rounded-full mx-auto object-cover border-4 border-white dark:border-gray-700 shadow-xl"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Profile Info -->
    <h1
        class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 text-center"
    >
        Hi, I'm <span class="text-brandingColor dark:text-blue-400"
            >Md Atiquzzaman Soikat</span
        >
    </h1>
    <p
        class="text-xl text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 font-semibold mb-6 text-center"
    >
        Senior Full Stack Developer | Team Lead
    </p>
    <div
        class="m-auto text-center mt-4 mb-4 justify-center flex flex-col items-center w-full space-x-5 space-y-8 lg:space-y-0 lg:flex-row"
    >
        <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/atiquzzaman-soikat/"
            aria-label="Connect on LinkedIn"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-2 py-2 font-black text-center text-white shadow-xl xl:px-12 xl:text-2xl lg:w-auto hover:bg-green-600 bg-blue-600 dark:bg-blue-700 dark:hover:bg-green-700"
        >
            Connect on LinkedIn
            <svg
                class="w-6 h-6 ml-2"
                aria-hidden="true"
                fill="currentColor"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
                <path
                    d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"
                ></path>
            </svg>
        </a>
        <a
            href="/resume.pdf"
            aria-label="View Resume"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-2 text-lg font-semibold border-2 border-gray-400 text-gray-700 dark:border-gray-500 dark:text-gray-200 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:text-blue-600 dark:hover:border-blue-300 dark:hover:text-blue-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-white dark:focus:ring-offset-gray-900"
            >View Resume</a
        >
    </div>
    <!-- Introduction -->
    <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        <p>
            I am a software developer with more than twelve years of experience
            focused on web technologies. My career has spanned diverse sectors,
            including education, hospitality, and most recently, retail. While
            my primary expertise lies in frontend development, I have
            progressively transitioned towards full-stack development and am
            actively cultivating expertise in DevOps.
        </p>
        <p>
            <span class="tech-highlight">JavaScript</span> has been my primary programming
            language throughout my career, complemented by experience in <span
                class="tech-highlight">TypeScript</span
            >, <span class="tech-highlight">PHP</span>, <span
                class="tech-highlight">Python</span
            >, and <span class="tech-highlight">Go</span>. While I've
            extensively worked with <span class="tech-highlight">React</span> and
            <span class="tech-highlight">Vue.js</span> and <span
                class="tech-highlight">Svelte</span
            >
            has emerged as my preferred frontend framework over the past few years,
            thanks to its elegant approach to UI development and exceptional developer
            experience.
        </p>
        <p>
            Beyond coding, I maintain a balanced life through gaming, cooking,
            and quality time with friends and family.
        </p>
        <section class="my-12 mx-auto max-w-4xl hidden">
            <div
                class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 via-brandingColor to-blue-600 overflow-hidden shadow-lg"
            >
                <div class="p-8 text-white">
                    <div
                        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between"
                    >
                        <div>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-2">
                                Have an idea?
                            </h2>
                            <div
                                class="text-2xl md:text-2xl font-extrabold mb-2"
                            >
                                Create an MVP in just <span class="relative">
                                    three weeks
                                    <svg
                                        class="absolute -bottom-1 left-0 w-full"
                                        height="4"
                                        viewBox="0 0 100 12"
                                        fill="none"
                                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                    >
                                        <path
                                            d="M1 5.5C20.6667 2.16667 68.3333 -0.499999 99 8.50001"
                                            stroke="white"
                                            stroke-width="3"
                                            stroke-linecap="round"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                </span>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <a
                            href="/services"
                            class="mt-6 md:mt-0 inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-white text-black font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-50 transition-colors shadow-md"
                        >
                            Learn More
                            <svg
                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                class="h-5 w-5 ml-2"
                                viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                                aria-hidden="true"
                                fill="currentColor"
                            >
                                <path
                                    fill-rule="evenodd"
                                    d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
                                    clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <style>
        :global(.tech-highlight) {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #142934;
        }

        :global(.dark .tech-highlight) {
            color: #dbeafe;
        }
    </style>
</MainLayout>
